name: ChaseCAT
tag_list: common-admission-test, mba-exam, entrance-exam-for-mba, mba-sample-papers, previous-papers, mba-admission, mba-admissions
overview:
ChaseCAT intends to help students prepare for MBA entrance and make the right decisions related to choosing a college for MBA.

ChaseCAT provides free online CAT style test papers on Verbal, Quant, Data Interpretation and Data Sufficiency. ChaseCAT provides detailed information about college placements, CAT cut-offs, live alumni profiles etc. It also provide multiple agency rankings to give a holistic picture. ChaseCAT also provides help on GD PI preparation for MBA entrance.
